# Personal account
IMAPAccount personal
Host imap.gmail.com
User ianprime0509@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass gmail-app-passwords/personal"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore personal-remote
Account personal

MaildirStore personal-local
Path ~/mail/personal/
Inbox ~/mail/personal/Inbox

Channel sync-personal
Master :personal-remote:
Slave :personal-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Slave
SyncState *
Expunge Both

Channel sync-personal-sent
Master :personal-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :personal-local:Sent
Create Slave
SyncState *
Expunge Both

Channel sync-personal-drafts
Master :personal-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :personal-local:Drafts
Create Slave
SyncState *
Expunge Both

Group personal
Channel sync-personal
Channel sync-personal-sent
Channel sync-personal-drafts

